casebody.data:
No.-.

Eisler v. United States. David Rein, Abraham J. Isserman and Joseph Forer for petitioner. Solicitor General Perlman for the United States.

The motion for an extension of time within which to file petition for. writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit is denied. Mr. Justice Frankfurter joins in denying this motion because the Court is without jurisdiction over the person of the petitioner.
